author: ozeigermann
msg: Removed global lock around fine grained locks as it was disabling the whole idea of fine grained locks. Before when there was a fine grained lock blocking another the global lock was still held as well disabling all other access.
Now this has been fixed and deadlocks are prevented by the same (numbered) sequence of locks acquired in all methods.
